## Algorithm

The AI uses the **Minimax algorithm with Alpha-Beta Pruning**:
- Evaluates all possible game states
- Maximizes AI's score while minimizing player's score
- Alpha-Beta pruning optimizes performance by eliminating unnecessary branches
- Makes the AI unbeatable in "Unbeatable" mode

## Installation
```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Run development server
npm run dev

# Build for production
npm run build
```

## How to Play

1. Choose difficulty: Easy or Unbeatable
2. Click any cell to place your X
3. AI will respond with O
4. Try to get three in a row!
5. In Unbeatable mode, the best you can do is draw!

## Technologies Used

- React
- JavaScript
- CSS3
- Vite

